20From%20Hijacked%20Train%20In%20Pakistan%2C%2027%20Rebels%20Killed%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Col%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20security%20forces%20managed%20to%20rescue%20155%20hostages%20after%20a%20gunfight%20with%20the%20rebels.%20The%20rescued%20passengers%20-%20including%C2%A0dozens%20of%20women%20and%20children%20-%C2%A0were%20taken%20to%20Mach%2C%20a%20nearby%20town%20where%20a%20makeshift%20hospital%20has%20been%20set%20up.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20gunfight%20between%20the%20rebels%20of%20the%20Balochistan%20Liberation%20Army%20(BLA)%20and%20the%20Pakistani%20forces%20continued%20overnight.%20It's%20not%20clear%20how%20many%20hostages%20remained%20on%20board%20Jaffar%20Express.%20The%20BLA%20has%20denied%20any%20casualties%20and%20claimed%20to%20have%20killed%2030%20soldiers%2C%20which%20has%20not%20been%20confirmed%20by%20authorities.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EA%20group%20of%20rebels%20was%20believed%20to%20have%20taken%20some%20of%20the%20hostages%20into%20the%20mountains%20and%20were%20being%20pursued%20by%20the%20security%20forces%2C%20while%20the%20rest%20were%20holding%20the%20locomotive.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EReports%20suggest%20they%20had%20split%20in%20small%20groups%20to%20try%20to%20escape%20in%20the%20dark%2C%20but%20the%20military%20forces%20said%20they%20surrounded%20the%20tunnel%20with%20the%20mountainous%20terrain%20posing%20difficulty%20to%20the%20security%20operation.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20Jaffar%20Express%20was%20intercepted%20by%20armed%20attackers%20in%20a%20tunnel%20in%20a%20remote%20area%20on%20its%20way%20from%20Quetta%20to%20Peshawar.%20At%20least%20400%20passengers%20were%20in%20its%20nine%20bogies.%20The%20route%20was%20made%20operational%20after%20a%20month-long%20suspension.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20hijacking%20was%20later%20claimed%20by%20the%20BLA%2C%20the%20strongest%20separatist%20group%20in%20the%20region%20seeking%20independence%20for%20Balochistan.%20They%20blew%20up%20the%20tracks%2C%20forcing%20it%20to%20come%20to%20a%20h