20for%20a%20full%20month-long%20ceasefire%20in%20a%20war%20that%20has%20claimed%20tens%20of%20thousands%20of%20lives.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BToday%20we%20made%20an%20offer%20that%20the%20Ukrainians%20have%20accepted%2C%20which%20is%20to%20enter%20into%20a%20ceasefire%20and%20into%20immediate%20negotiations%2C%26quot%3B%20US%20Secretary%20of%20State%20Marco%20Rubio%20told%20reporters%20after%20around%20nine%20hours%20of%20talks%20in%20an%20ornate%20hotel%20in%20Jeddah.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe'll%20take%20this%20offer%20now%20to%20the%20Russians%20and%20we%20hope%20they'll%20say%20yes%20to%20peace.%20The%20ball%20is%20now%20in%20their%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20they%20say%20no%20then%20we'll%2C%20unfortunately%2C%20know%20what%20the%20impediment%20is%20to%20peace%20here%2C%26quot%3B%20Rubio%20said%20of%20Russia%2C%20which%20launched%20a%20full-scale%20invasion%20of%20its%20smaller%20neighbour%20in%20February%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERubio%20said%20the%20United%20States%20would%20immediately%20resume%20military%20assistance%20and%20intelligence%20sharing%20it%20had%20cut%20off%20to%20pressure%20its%20wartime%20partner%20following%20a%20disastrous%20February%2028%20meeting%20between%20Trump%20and%20President%20Volodymyr%20Zelensky.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Washington%2C%20Trump%20said%20he%20was%20ready%20to%20welcome%20Zelensky%20back%20to%20the%20White%20House%20and%20may%20speak%20to%20President%20Vladimir%20Putin%20this%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20by%20a%20reporter%20about%20the%20prospects%20of%20a%20comprehensive%20ceasefire%20in%20Ukraine%2C%20Trump%20answered%3A%20%26quot%3BWell%2C%20I%20hope%20it%20will%20be%20over%20the%20next%20few%20days%2C%20I'd%20like%20to%20see.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20know%20we%20have%20a%20big%20meeting%20with%20Russia%20tomorrow%20and%20some%20great%20conversations%20hopefully%20will%20ensue.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20joint%20statement%2C%20Ukraine%20and%20the%20United%20States%20said%20they%20would%20conclude%20%26quot%3Bas%20soon%20as%20possible%26quot%3B%20a%20deal%20securing%20US%20access%20to%20Ukraine's%20mineral%20wealth%2C%20which%20Trump%20demanded%20as%20compensation%20for%20billions%20of%20dollars%20in%20US%20weapons%20under%20his%20predecessor%20Joe%20Biden.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EZelensky%20was%20supposed%20to%20sign%20the%20deal%20at%20the%20White%20House%20before%20the%20dramatic%20on-camera%20showdown%2C%20in%20which%20Trump%20and%20Vice%20President%20JD%20Vance%20dressed%20down%20the%20wartime%20leader%20and%20accused%20him%20of%20ingratitude.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EZelensky%20quickly%20thanked%20Trump%20over%20the%20%26quot%3Bpositive%26quot%3B%20ceasefire%20proposal%20made%20in%20Jeddah%20and%20said%20the%20United%20States%20must%20now%20work%20to%20persuade%20Russia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20American%20side%20understands%20our%20arguments%2C%20perceives%20our%20proposals%2C%20and%20I%20want%20to%20thank%20President%20Trump%20for%20the%20constructive%20conversation%20between%20our%20teams%2C%26quot%3B%20Zelensky%20said%20in%20his%20evening%20address.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E-%20Russia%20must%20respond%20'clearly'%20-%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20the%20US%20cutoff%20of%20aid%20and%20intelligence%20sharing%2C%20Russia%20has%20stepped%20up%20attacks%20on%20Ukraine's%20energy%20infrastructure%20and%20seized%20back%20land%20in%20Russia's%20Kursk%20region%20which%20Ukrainian%20forces%20had%20infiltrated%20as%20they%20seek%20leverage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHours%20before%20the%20Jeddah%20talks%2C%20Ukraine%20staged%20a%20major%20direct%20attack%20on%20Moscow%2C%20with%20hundreds%20of%20drones%20slamming%20into%20the%20capital%20and%20other%20areas%2C%20leaving%20three%20people%20dead.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETop%20Zelensky%20aide%20Andriy%20Yermak%20said%20in%20Jeddah%20that%20Ukraine%20had%20made%20clear%20that%20its%20desire%20is%20peace.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRussia%20needs%20to%20say%2C%20very%20clearly%2C%20they%20want%20peace%20or%20not%2C%20they%20want%20to%20end%20this%20war%2C%20which%20they%20started%2C%20or%20no%2C%26quot%3B%20Yermak%20told%20reporters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump's%20abrupt%20shift%20on%20Ukraine%20following%20Biden's%20strong%20support%20has%20rattled%20European%20allies%2C%20with%20France%20and%20Germany%20increasingly%20speaking%20of%20developing%20common%20European%20defence%20if%20the%20United%20States%20no%20longer%20offers%20its%20security%20guarantees%20through%20NATO.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20Mike%20Waltz%2C%20Trump's%20national%20security%20advisor%2C%20countered%20that%20the%20brash%20president%20has%20%26quot%3Bliterally%20moved%20the%20entire%20global%20conversation%26quot%3B%20in%20support%20of%20peace.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe've%20gone%20from%20if%20the%20war%20is%20going%20to%20end%20to%20how%20the%20war%20is%20going%20to%20end%2C%26quot%3B%20Waltz%20told%20reporters%20alongside%20Rubio.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWaltz%2C%20who%20said%20he%20would%20speak%20in%20the%20coming%20days%20with%20his%20Russian%20counterpart%2C%20credited%20the%20Ukrainians%20with%20agreeing%20on%20the%20need%20to%20%26quot%3Bend%20the%20killing%2C%20to%20end%20the%20tragic%20meat-grinder%20of%20people%20and%20national%20treasure%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E-%20Allies%20cautious%20-%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERubio%20will%20head%20Wednesday%20to%20Canada%20--%20another%20country%20with%20which%20Trump%20is%20feuding%20--%20to%20meet%20fellow%20foreign%20ministers%20of%20the%20Group%20of%20Seven%20industrial%20democracies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERubio%20has%20said%20he%20will%20push%20the%20G7%20to%20avoid%20%26quot%3Bantagonistic%26quot%3B%20language%20about%20Russia%20for%20fear%20of%20scuttling%20diplomacy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Poland%2C%20a%20top%20supporter%20of%20Ukraine%20and%20where%20historical%20memories%20of%20Russia%20run%20deep%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Donald%20Tusk%20praised%20the%20%26quot%3B