Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20any%20expectations%20that%20the%20start%20of%20Trump's%20new%20term%20would%20continue%20to%20fuel%20market%20returns%20have%20been%20upended.%20The%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20has%20lost%206.4%25%20since%20he%20took%20office%2C%20as%20mass%20layoffs%20of%20government%20employees%20and%20the%20president's%20back-and-forth%20on%20tariffs%20have%20roiled%20equities%2C%20with%20the%20benchmark%20index%20tumbling%202.7%25%20on%20Monday.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20companies%20behind%20the%20inauguration%20attendees'%20fortunes%20have%20been%20some%20of%20the%20biggest%20losers%2C%20dropping%20a%20combined%20%241.39%20trillion%20in%20market%20value%20since%20Jan.%2017%2C%20the%20last%20trading%20day%20before%20the%20inauguration.%20Here's%20a%20look%20at%20some%20of%20those%20fortunes%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EElon%20Musk%20(down%20%24148%20billion)%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2053-year-old%20Tesla%20chief%20executive%20officer's%20net%20worth%20peaked%20at%20%24486%20billion%20on%20Dec.%2017%2C%20the%20largest%20fortune%20ever%20recorded%20on%20Bloomberg's%20wealth%20index.%20Most%20of%20his%20gains%20came%20from%20Tesla%2C%20whose%20stock%20nearly%20doubled%20after%20the%20election.%20Since%20then%2C%20the%20electric%20carmaker%20has%20given%20up%20all%20of%20those%20gains.%20Consumers%20in%20Europe%20have%20soured%20on%20Musk's%20support%20for%20far-right%20politicians%2C%20with%20Tesla%20sales%20in%20Germany%20falling%20by%20more%20than%2070%25%20in%20the%20first%20two%20months%20of%20the%20year.%20Chinese%20shipments%20also%20fell%20by%2049%25%20last%20month%20to%20levels%20not%20seen%20since%20July%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EJeff%20Bezos%20(down%20%2429%20billion)%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBezos%2C%2061%2C%20who%20clashed%20with%20Trump%20over%20the%20postal%20service%20and%20his%20ownership%20of%20the%20Washington%20Post%20during%20the%20president's%20first%20term%2C%20congratulated%20Trump%20the%20day%20af