highly%20nutritious%20puppy%20food%20options%2C%20including%20those%20for%20large%20and%20small%20breed%20puppies%2C%20in%20our%20guide%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fpets%2Fbest-puppy-food%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebest%20puppy%20foods%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2224e4d3f6-f5e9-4004-88bd-6eed528ae849%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Best%20for%20small%20dogs%5C%22%3EBest%20for%20small%20dogs%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20experts%20say%20the%20best%20and%20cheapest%20dog%20food%20for%20small%20dogs%20should%20have%20small%20kibbles%20for%20easy%20chewing%2C%20be%20calorie-dense%20to%20support%20their%20higher%20metabolism%2C%20and%2C%20like%20all%20the%20foods%20on%20this%20list%2C%20be%20either%20formulated%20to%20meet%20the%20AAFCO%20nutritional%20standards%20or%20tested%20through%20feeding%20trials%20to%20ensure%20safety%20and%20nutrition.%20Based%20on%20this%20advice%2C%20our%20top%20recommendation%20is%20Blue%20Buffalo%20Life%20Protection%20Formula%20Small%20Breed%20Adult%20Chicken%20and%20Brown%20Rice%20Recipe.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDogs%20rely%20on%20a%20healthy%20balance%20of%20protein%2C%20fats%2C%20and%20carbohydrates%20to%20power%20through%20their%20days.%20Our%20top%20pick%20for%20small%20breeds%20delivers%20these%20essential%20nutrients%20in%20bite-sized%20pieces%20perfect%20for%20smaller%20mouths.%20Antioxidant-rich%20ingredients%20like%20sweet%20potatoes%2C%20blueberries%2C%20and%20cranberries%20may%20help%20support%20liver%2C%20kidney%2C%20and%20brain%20health.%20Plus%2C%20sweet%20potatoes%20and%20chicory%20root%20provide%20beneficial%20fiber%20for%20healthy%20digestion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBlue%20Buffalo%20was%20founded%20in%202003%2C%20inspired%20by%20a%20beloved%20Airedale%20Terrier%20named%20Blue.%20Today%2C%20the%20brand%20is%20owned%20by%20General%20Mills%20and%20is%20available%20in%20all%2050%20states%20and%20numerous%20countries%20at%20pet%20stores%2C%20supermarkets%2C%20and%20online%20retailers.%20For%20more%20inexpensive%20foods%20for%20pups%20of%20all%20ages%2C%20check%20out%20our%20guide%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fpets%2Fbest-dog-food-small-dogs%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebest%20dog%20food%20for%20small%20breeds%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%227ada79ac-dc42-4f8d-884a-1e5b623bbf91%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Best%20for%20large%20dogs%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EBest%20for%20large%20dogs%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ECanned%20foods%20aren't%20the%20cheapest%20dog%20food%2C%20and%20costs%20can%20add%20up%20even%20quicker%20when%20you're%20feeding%20a%20large%20breed.%20To%20keep%20expenses%20down%20without%20sacrificing%20nutrition%2C%20we%20recommend%20Iams%20Proactive%20Health%20Large%20Breed%20Chicken%20and%20Whole%20Grain%20Rice%20Recipe.%20The%20large%20kibbles%20encourage%20dogs%20to%20chew%2C%20preventing%20big%20dogs%20from%20gulping%20down%20their%20meal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20recipe%20features%20chicken%20and%20chicken%20meal%20as%20high-quality%20protein%20sources%2C%20with%20the%20chicken%20meal%20form%20also%20being%20a%20good%20source%20of%20glucosamine%20and%20chondroitin.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Fin%2Falejandro-caos-76468a102%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDr.%20Alejandro%20Caos%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20small%20animal%20veterinarian%20at%20Silver%20Bluff%20Animal%20Clinic%2C%20says%20these%20nutrients%20may%20support%20joint%20health%20and%20mobility%2C%20which%20is%20especially%20important%20for%20larger%20dogs%20prone%20to%20joint%20issues%20like%20hip%20dysplasia%20and%20arthritis.%20It%20also%20contains%20dried%20beet%20pulp%2C%20a%20great%20source%20of%20fermentable%20fiber%20that%20helps%20keep%20digestion%20regular%20and%20promotes%20a%20lasting%20feeling%20of%20fullness%20between%20meals.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20recipe%20contains%20353%20calories%20per%20cup.%20Like%20most%20dry%20foods%2C%20it's%20calorie-dense%2C%20meaning%20one%20bag%20lasts%20for%20many%20meals.%20Caos%20says%20portion%20control%20is%20essential%20to%20prevent%20overfeeding%20and%20weight%20gain%2C%20which%20can%20exacerbate%20joint%20issues%20in%20large-breed%20dogs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMars%2C%20Incorporated%20owns%20Iams%20and%20distributes%20its%20pet%20food%20in%20more%20than%2040%20countries.%20The%20company%20also%20manufactures%20the%20well-regarded%20premium%20pet%20food%20brands%20Royal%20Canin%20and%20Eukanuba.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f3842fcb-4615-4dd4-b5fa-eccf791ea1bc%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Best%20for%20senior%20dogs%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EBest%20for%20senior%20dogs%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20best%20budget-friendly%20dog%20foods%20for%20seniors%20are%20formulated%20to%20meet%20their%20nutritional%20needs%20and%20also%20help%20manage%20age-related%20conditions%20like%20decreased%20mobility%2C%20muscle%20loss%2C%20and%20cognitive%20decline.%20While%20large%20breed%20dogs%20may%20enter%20their%20senior%20years%20around%205%20years%20old%2C%20smaller%20breeds%20typically%20reach%20this%20stage%20around%2010.%20Whatever%20your%20dog's%20size%2C%20Iams%20ProActive%20Health%20Healthy%20Aging%20Chicken%20and%20Whole%20Grain%20Recipe%20delivers%20key%20ingredients%20for%20many%20enjoyable%20golden%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20dry%20food%20for%20older%20dogs%20contains%20marine%20microalgae%2C%20a%20more%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.liebertpub.com%2Fdoi%2Fabs%2F10.1089%2Find.2017.29102.wmo%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esustainable%20source%20of%20omega%20fatty%20acids%3C%2Fa%3E%20than%20fish%20oil.%20Whole%20grain%20carbohydrates%20provide%20energy%20for%20your%20young-at-heart%20senior%2C%20while%20beet%20pulp%20aids%20digestion.%20L-carnitine%20helps%20prevent%20weight%20gain%20and%20preserve%20muscle%20mass%2C%20alongside%20a%20healthy%20serving%20of%20chicken%20and%20chicken%20byproduct%20meal.%20To%20round%20out%20this%20senior%20recipe%2C%20antioxidant-rich%20carrots%20may%20help%20combat%20oxidative%20damage%2C%20reducing%20the%20risk%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpmc.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2Farticles%2FPMC2390776%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elearning%20and%20memory%20decline%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20senior%20dogs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20guide%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fpets%2Fbest-senior-dog-food%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebest%20senior%20dog%20food%3C%2Fa%3E%20includes%20more%20recommendations%20in%20wet%20and%20dry%20recipes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22da1ee080-ba1e-48f0-8542-dc94a4d973e3%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22What%20to%20look%20for%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20to%20look%20for%20in%20budget-friendly%20dog%20foods%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20shopping%20for%20the%20best%20budget-friendly%20dog%20foods%2C%20there's%20no%20need%20to%20cut%20corners.%20Focus%20on%20the%20essential%20qualities%20below%20that%20make%20any%20dog%20food%20a%20quality%20choice.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAAFCO%20nutritional%20adequacy%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20Association%20of%20American%20Feed%20Control%20Officials%20(AAFCO)%20is%20a%20nonprofit%20organization%20that%20determines%20nutritional%20standards%20for%20pet%20food.%20Every%20food%20we%20recommend%20includes%20a%20statement%20on%20the%20label%20confirming%20it%20meets%20the%20AAFCO's%20nutritional%20standards%20through%20formulation%20or%20feed%20trial%20testing.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20important%20because%20it%20helps%20owners%20identify%20whether%20a%20pet%20food%20is%20complete%20and%20balanced%20for%20their%20pet's%20life%20stage%2C%26quot%3B%20Vasudevan%20says.%20You%20can%20learn%20more%20about%20the%20AAFCO%20standards%20in%20our%20guide%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fpets%2Fbest-dog-food%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebest%20dog%20foods%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWSAVA%20nutrition%20guidelines%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwsava.org%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWorld%20Small%20Animal%20Veterinary%20Association%20(WSAVA)%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20a%20global%20network%20of%20veterinary%20professionals%20dedicated%20to%20improving%20the%20health%20and%20welfare%20of%20companion%20animals%20%E2%80%94%20not%20just%20through%20nutrition%2C%20but%20by%20also%20considering%20disease%20prevention%20and%20management%2C%20says%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.lovet.com%2Flocations%2Fil%2Fchicago%2F802-w-fulton-market%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDr.%20Caitlin%20Johnson%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20veterinarian%20at%20Lovet%20Pet%20Health%20Care.%20The%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwsava.org%2Fglobal-guidelines%2Fglobal-nutrition-guidelines%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGlobal%20Nutrition%20Guidelines%3C%2Fa%3E%20published%20by%20WSAVA%20help%20veterinarians%20and%20pet%20owners%20make%20informed%20decisions%20about%20pet%20food.%20%26quot%3BThey%20recommend%20selecting%20brands%20that%20employ%20veterinary%20nutritionists%2C%20conduct%20feeding%20trials%2C%20and%20follow%20strict%20quality%20control%20and%20safety%20testing%2C%26quot%3B%20Vasudevan%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EGuaranteed%20analysis%20and%20calories%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Johnson%20says%20a%20food's%20overall%20nutrient%20profile%20is%20more%20important%20than%20nitpicking%20its%20individual%20ingredients.%20You%20can%20find%20the%20nutrient%20profile%20in%20the%20guaranteed%20analysis%20on%20the%20pet%20food%20label%2C%20including%20the%20minimum%20protein%20and%20fat%20levels%20and%20the%20maximum%20fiber%20and%20moisture.%20Calorie%20content%20varies%20widely%20across%20food%20types%20and%20brands%20and%20is%20listed%20as%20kilocalories%20(kcal)%20per%20cup%20or%20ounce%20on%20dog%20food%20labels.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBrand%20reputation%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EWeeth%20says%20the%20best%20budget-friendly%20dog%20food%20brands%20have%2020%20years%20or%20more%20of%20experience%20in%20pet%20food%20manufacturing%20and%20sales.%20This%20gives%20you%20more%20insight%20into%20their%20track%20record%2C%20including%20pet%20food%20recalls.%20Johnson%20says%20most%20veterinarians%20recommend%20the%20%26quot%3Bbig%20four%20brands%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20Hill's%2C%20Royal%20Canin%2C%20Purina%2C%20and%20Eukanuba%20%E2%80%94%20and%20she%20would%20add%20budget-friendly%20Iams%20Proactive%20Health%20to%20that%20list%20as%20well.%20All%20of%20these%20brands%20employ%20board-certified%20veterinary%20nutritionists%20to%20ensure%20their%20food%20is%20balanced%20and%20safe%20for%20consumption%2C%20she%20says.%20While%20Eukanuba%20and%20Royal%20Canin%20are%20reputable%20brands%2C%20their%20prices%20rise%20above%20a%20budget-friendly%20price%20range%2C%20so%20we%20didn't%20include%20them%20in%20this%20guide.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EManufacturing%20standards%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20When%20choosing%20dog%20food%2C%20consider%20the%20brand's%20manufacturing%20standards%20and%20quality%20control%20measures.%20Weeth%20says%20brands%20that%20own%20their%20own%20manufacturing%20facilities%20have%20greater%20oversight%20of%20their%20ingredients%20and%20production%20processes.%20Some%20brands%20share%20this%20information%20on%20their%20websites%20as%20part%20of%20their%20transparency%20pledge.%20If%20you%20can't%20find%20it%20online%2C%20you%20may%20need%20to%20reach%20out%20to%20the%20company%20directly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWeeth%20says%20to%20also%20consider%20a%20brand's%20distribution%20reach.%20Companies%20that%20only%20sell%20locally%20may%20face%20fewer%20regulatory%20requirements%20than%20those%20that%20distribute%20nationally.%20Brands%20sold%20at%20major%20retailers%20like%20Amazon%20and%20Chewy%20ship%20to%20all%2048%20contiguous%20states%2C%20which%20means%20they%20must%20comply%20with%20the%20strictest%20regulations.%20This%20provides%20an%20added%20layer%20of%20quality%20assurance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIngredients%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EBecause%20dogs%20are%20omnivores%2C%20a%20balanced%20recipe%20will%20include%20proteins%2C%20fats%2C%20and%20carbohydrates.%20Just%20as%20important%20as%20what's%20included%20in%20your%20dog's%20food%20is%20what's%20left%20out.%20For%20instance%2C%20Johnson%20says%20grain-free%20diets%20have%20become%20a%20popular%20fad%2C%20often%20marketed%20as%20a%20solution%20for%20allergies.%20However%2C%20these%20diets%20have%20been%20linked%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.fda.gov%2Fanimal-veterinary%2Foutbreaks-and-advisories%2Ffda-investigation-potential-link-between-certain-diets-and-canine-dilated-cardiomyopathy%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edilated%20cardiomyopathy%20(DCM)%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20preventable%20heart%20disease%20in%20dogs.%20In%20addition%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnow.tufts.edu%2F2017%2F04%2F10%2Fgrain-free-diet-healthier-my-dogs-and-cats%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETufts%20University%20says%3C%2Fa%3E%20grains%20provide%20essential%20plant-based%20protein%2C%20fiber%2C%20and%20fatty%20acids%2C%20making%20them%20a%20valuable%20part%20of%20the%20canine%20diet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDon't%20be%20put%20off%20by%20recipes%20that%20contain%20byproducts%2C%20Weeth%20says.%20Byproducts%20and%20meat%20meals%20are%20nutritious%20organ%20meats%2C%20such%20as%20hearts%2C%20spleens%2C%20and%20livers.%20Some%20brands%20market%20their%20food%20as%20%26quot%3Bbyproduct-free%26quot%3B%20while%20still%20including%20organ%20meats%20in%20the%20ingredient%20list.%20When%20a%20recipe%20specifies%20ingredients%20like%20%26quot%3Bbeef%20liver%2C%26quot%3B%20Weeth%20says%20it's%20still%20using%20byproducts%2C%20just%20listing%20them%20individually%2C%20which%20can%20drive%20up%20the%20cost.%20Ingredient%20lists%20that%20include%20%26quot%3Bbyproducts%26quot%3B%20or%20%26quot%3Bmeals%26quot%3B%20are%20formulated%20using%20the%20most%20cost-effective%20options%20available%20at%20the%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20may%20be%20tempting%20to%20splurge%20on%20dog%20food%20that%20includes%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ams.usda.gov%2Fservices%2Fgrading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUS%20Department%20of%20Agriculture%20(USDA)%20graded%20meats%20%3C%2Fa%3Eor%20human-grade%20ingredients%2C%20but%20Vasudevan%20says%20it's%20not%20necessary.%20%26quot%3BThey%20don't%20always%20equate%20to%20better%20nutrition%20for%20pets%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20says.%20The%20main%20difference%20lies%20in%20handling%20and%20storage.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhuman-grade-pet-food-on-the-rise-owners-ditch-kibble-2023-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHuman-grade%20ingredients%3C%2Fa%3E%20must%20comply%20with%20USDA%20regulations%20and%20be%20made%20in%20USDA-inspected%20facilities.%20Non-human-grade%20ingredients%20are%20regulated%20by%20the%20US%20Food%20and%20Drug%20Administration%20(FDA)%2C%20and%20the%20safety%20standards%20may%20be%20less%20stringent.%20While%20pet%20foods%20made%20through%20either%20route%20are%20safe%2C%20if%20your%20pet%20has%20severe%20allergies%20or%20digestive%20issues%2C%20you%20might%20choose%20human-grade%20food%20for%20its%20stringent%20quality%20control%20and%20production%20standards.%20For%20more%20about%20pet%20food%20made%20with%20human-grade%20ingredients%2C%20check%20out%20our%20guide%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fpets%2Fbest-fresh-dog-food%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebest%20fresh%20dog%20food%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPrice%20per%20pound%20and%20feeding%20guidelines%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ETo%20compare%20the%20cost%20of%20dry%20food%20(priced%20per%20pound)%20and%20wet%20food%20(priced%20per%20ounce)%2C%20you'll%20need%20to%20determine%20how%20much%20your%20dog%20will%20eat%2C%20as%20portion%20sizes%20vary%20depending%20on%20the%20food's%20calorie%20content.%20You%20can%20refer%20to%20the%20feeding%20guidelines%20on%20the%20label%20or%20bag%20to%20estimate%20how%20many%20servings%20are%20in%20a%20can%20or%20bag.%20However%2C%20these%20recommendations%20are%20just%20rough%20estimates.%20Your%20veterinarian%20can%20help%20determine%20the%20best%20daily%20calorie%20intake%20for%20your%20dog%20based%20on%20their%20age%2C%20health%2C%20and%20target%20weight.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAuto-shipping%20discounts%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EYou%20can%20save%20even%20more%20money%20on%20pet%20food%20when%20you%20order%20from%20some%20online%20retailers.%20Sites%20like%20Chewy%2C%20Amazon%2C%20and%20Petco%20offer%20discounts%20on%20recurring%20shipments%20or%20subscription%20plans.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22fe8665a4-4716-44ca-aa10-9892f75c8ce2%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22How%20we%20selected%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20we%20selected%20the%20best%20budget-friendly%20dog%20food%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20been%20covering%20the%20pet%20food%20beat%20for%20Business%20Insider%20Reviews%20since%202023%20and%20have%20spoken%20to%20several%20veterinary%20nutritionists%20about%20what%20to%20look%20for%20in%20high-quality%20dog%20and%20cat%20food.%20For%20this%20guide%2C%20I%20consulted%20a%20veterinary%20nutritionist%20and%20four%20small%20animal%20veterinarians%20for%20this%20guide.%20These%20experts%20didn't%20recommend%20specific%20foods%2C%20but%20they%20helped%20me%20determine%20what%20makes%20a%20quality%20dog%20food%20and%20how%20you%20can%20feed%20your%20dog%20in%20a%20safe%20and%20affordable%20way.%20I%20also%20followed%20the%20standards%20from%20the%20AAFCO%2C%20the%20WSAVA%20Global%20Nutrition%20Guidelines%2C%20and%20the%20guidance%20of%20other%20publications%20and%20organizations%20linked%20in%20this%20article.%20These%20resources%20helped%20me%20assess%20brand%20reputation%20through%20quality%20control%20standards%20and%20recipe%20formulation.%20Finally%2C%20I%20considered%20each%20food's%20cost%20per%20pound%20or%20ounce%2C%20weighing%20price%20tags%20against%20ingredient%20quality%2C%20nutritional%20value%2C%20and%20feeding%20guidelines.%20All%20of%20my%20recommendations%20offer%20a%20great%20balance%20of%20affordability%2C%20nutrition%2C%20and%20convenience.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%228b21ffee-117c-4231-8499-ac61a994c68d%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22FAQs%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EBudget-friendly%20dog%20food%20FAQs%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Ch3%3EWhat%20should%20I%20feed%20my%20dog%20on%20a%20budget%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EDry%20dog%20food%2C%20also%20called%20kibble%2C%20is%20often%20more%20affordable%20than%20wet%20food.%20However%2C%20our%20experts%20say%20the%20most%20important%20factor%2C%20regardless%20of%20cost%2C%20is%20that%20the%20food%20is%20complete%20and%20balanced%20for%20your%20dog%2C%20which%20is%20indicated%20by%20an%20AAFCO%20statement%20on%20the%20packaging.%20Johnson%20says%20veterinarians%20often%20recommend%20Hill's%2C%20Purina%2C%20and%20Iams%2C%20as%20these%20brands%20employ%20board-certified%20veterinary%20nutritionists%20and%20offer%20a%20range%20of%20recipes%2C%20including%20options%20for%20specific%20health%20needs%20and%20budgets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EWhat%20is%20the%20difference%20between%20high-quality%20and%20low-quality%20dog%20food%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20experts%20say%20high-quality%20dog%20food%2C%20regardless%20of%20price%2C%20meets%20the%20AAFCO%20nutritional%20standards%2C%20which%20include%20a%20balanced%20mix%20of%20proteins%2C%20fats%2C%20carbohydrates%2C%20and%20beneficial%20fibers.%20It%20also%20adheres%20to%20the%20nutritional%20guidelines%20published%20by%20WSAVA%20and%20comes%20from%20a%20well-established%20brand%20known%20for%20its%20consistency%20and%20product%20quality.%20On%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20low-quality%20diets%20are%20often%20not%20nutritionally%20complete%20and%20balanced%20and%20may%20include%20fad%20or%20boutique%20options%20like%20grain-free%20diets%2C%20Johnson%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EWho%20has%20the%20cheapest%20dog%20food%20prices%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20general%2C%20online%20retailers%20such%20as%20Amazon%20and%20Chewy%20have%20the%20most%20competitive%20pricing%20on%20dog%20food.%20You%20can%20save%20even%20more%20by%20signing%20up%20for%20recurring%20shipments%20or%20subscription%20plans%2C%20which%20often%20offer%20small%20discounts%20and%20the%20convenience%20of%20scheduled%20deliveries.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cspan%3EWhat%20is%20the%20best%20way%20to%20switch%20a%20dog's%20food%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20best%20way%20to%20switch%20your%20dog's%20food%20without%20digestive%20upset%20is%20to%20follow%20a%20slow%20transition%20spanning%20about%20a%20week.%20%26quot%3BWe%20aim%20for%20a%20ratio%20of%2075%3A25%20old%20food%20to%20new%20food%20for%202%20to%203%20days%2C%20then%2050%3A50%20ratio%20for%202%20to%203%20days%2C%20then%20a%2025%3A75%20ratio%20for%202%20to%203%20days%2C%20then%20going%20100%25%20in%20with%20the%20new%20food%2C%26quot%3B%20Johnson%20says.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22eae3e843-59f1-4212-a1cb-eca872cd89a0%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2295c1615d-65c0-4df2-ae5c-20cec5957385%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fpets%2Fbest-budget-friendly-dog-foods%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1741724633000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67d09873585f1dff88b1d162%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fpets%2Fbest-budget-friendly-dog-foods%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22You%20can%20feed%20your%20dog%20a%20healthy%20diet%20with%20one%20of%20the%20best%20budget-friendly%20dog%20foods.%20Our%20top%20wet%20and%20dry%20foods%20are%20for%20large%20breeds%2C%20seniors%20and%20more.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Janelle%20Leeson%2CSorin%20McKnight)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fpets%2Fbest-budget-friendly-dog-foods%22%2C