%20been%20ripped%20off%20from%20every%20nation%20in%20the%20world%2C%20every%20company%20in%20the%20world.%20We've%20been%20ripped%20off%20at%20levels%20never%20seen%20before%2C%20and%20what%20we're%20going%20to%20do%20is%20get%20it%20back%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%20has%20imposed%20tariffs%20on%20Mexico%2C%20Canada%2C%20and%20China%2C%20citing%20the%20countries'%20alleged%20border%20control%20issues%20leading%20to%20fentanyl%20pouring%20into%20the%20US%20and%20killing%20American%20citizens%2C%20Fox%20News%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20on%20March%207%2C%20Trump%20delayed%20tariffs%20on%20Mexico%20and%20Canada%20for%20a%20short-term%20period%20for%20certain%20products%20before%20the%20%26quot%3Bbig%20one%26quot%3B%20from%20April%202.%20He%20said%20he%20agreed%20after%20having%20%26quot%3Bfruitful%20conversations%26quot%3B%20with%20Mexico%20President%20Claudia%20Sheinbaum%20while%20he%20slammed%20Canada%20for%20being%20a%20%26quot%3Bhigh%20tariff%20nation%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20week%2C%20Trump%20attacked%20India's%20tariffs%2C%20saying%20it%20is%20%26quot%3Bnext%20to%20impossible%20to%20sell%20anything%20to%20India%26quot%3B%20because%20of%20the%20%26quot%3Bhigh%20tariffs.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20nationally%20televised%20address%2C%20Trump%20focused%20on%20the%20tariffs%20his%20administration%20will%20be%20putting%20in%20effect%20soon.%20However%2C%20he%20also%20revealed%20that%20India%20has%20agreed%20to%20slash%20its%20tariffs%20significantly%2C%20allegedly%20because%20%26quot%3Bsomebody%20is%20finally%20exposing%20them%20for%20what%20they%20have%20done.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20remarks%20at%20the%20White%20House%2C%20Trump%20stated%2C%20%26quot%3BIndia%20charges%20us%20massive%20tariffs.%20Massive.%20You%20can't%20even%20sell%20anything%20in%20India...They%20have%20agreed%2C%20by%20the%20way%3B%20they%20want%20to%20cut%20their%20tariffs%20way%20down%20now%20because%20somebody%20is%2