%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20US%20Navy's%20shipbuilding%20muscles%20have%20atrophied%2C%20leaving%20it%20with%20a%20serious%20problem%20amid%20China's%20massive%20military%20buildup.%3Cp%3EThiep%20Nguyen%2FUS%20Navy%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EAllies%20South%20Korea%20and%20Japan%20have%20robust%20shipbuilding%20industries.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHow%20they%20manage%20their%20shipyards%20and%20workforce%2C%20as%20well%20as%20build%20vessels%2C%20offer%20potential%20solutions%20for%20US%20yards.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ESouth%20Korea%20and%20Japan%20are%20the%20second%20and%20third%20biggest%20commercial%20builders%20behind%20China.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EFixing%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-shipbuilding-problems-could-be-navys-achilles-heel-china-war-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUS%20shipbuilding%3C%2Fa%3E%20problems%20and%20revitalizing%20American%20seapower%20has%20become%20a%20top%20priority.%20A%20pair%20of%20Pacific%20allies%20with%20strong%20industries%20might%20have%20answers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESouth%20Korea%20and%20Japan%20are%20major%20shipbuilders%2C%20and%20US%20yards%20constructing%20Navy%20ships%20could%20learn%20from%20their%20approaches%2C%20a%20veteran%20naval%20affairs%20expert%20told%20lawmakers%20this%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20statement%20to%20the%20House%20Armed%20Services%20Committee's%20Seapower%20and%20Projection%20Forces%20subcommittee%2C%20expert%20naval%20affairs%20specialist%20Robert%20O'Rourke%20highlighted%20the%20success%20that%20allies%20like%20South%20Korea%20and%20Japan%20have%20seen%20in%20shipbuilding.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETheir%20approaches%20include%20in-house%20worker%20training%20that%20can%20address%20capability%2C%20operations%2C%20and%20materials%20management%20issues%2C%20such%20as%20%26quot%3Bmonitoring%20and%20managing%20the%20flow%20of%20work%20through%20the%20shipyard%20on%20a%20continuous%20basis%2C%26quot%3B%20O'Rourke%2C%20a%20longtime%20Congressional%20Research%20Service%20analyst%2C%20said%20in%20written%20testimony.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Two%20vessels%20are%20seen%20at%20a%20South%20Korean%20shipyard%2C%20with%20various%20equipment%20and%20cranes%20surrounding%20them.%20A%20city%20is%20seen%20in%20the%20background.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67d08334b8b41a9673fa4edf%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222800%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EOne%20solution%20presented%20was%20looking%20at%20South%20Korea%20and%20Japan's%20management%20of%20their%20yards%20and%20workforces.%3Cp%3ENurPhoto%2FNurPhoto%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20also%20embrace%20effective%20design%20and%20construction%20processes.%20South%20Korea%2C%20for%20instance%2C%20designs%20%26quot%3Bship%20sections%20with%20a%20strong%20focus%20on%20reducing%20the%20labor%20hours%20needed%20to%20produce%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20O'Rouke%20said.%20Doing%20so%20could%20mean%20enlarging%20ship%20sections%20to%20improve%20worker%20access%20to%20spaces%20and%20using%20straighter%2C%20less%20convoluted%20pipe%20runs%20%26quot%3Bthat%20take%20up%20more%20space%20but%20require%20less%20labor%20to%20produce%20and%20install.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20cost%20for%20bigger%20ship%20sections%20would%20be%20higher%2C%20but%20the%20reduction%20in%20labor%20costs%20more%20than%20offsets%20it.%20The%20end%20result%20could%20make%20ships%20much%20%26quot%3Beasier%20and%20less%20expensive%20to%20build%2C%20maintain%2C%20and%20modernize%20over%20their%20life%20cycles%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20a%20congressional%20hearing%20Thursday%2C%20O'Rourke%20said%20that%20there%20were%20lessons%20to%20be%20learned%20from%20both%20Japan%20and%20South%20Korea's%20shipbuilding%20models%20and%20that%20the%20two%20were%20mentioned%20%26quot%3Balmost%20side-by-side%26quot%3B%20when%20discussing%20best%20practices%20for%20world-class%20shipbuilding%20standards%20for%20efficient%20shipyard%20operations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20topic%20of%20discussion%20has%20revolved%20around%20how%20Japan%20maintains%20a%20steady%20procurement%20rate%20amid%20changes%20in%20force%20size%2C%20a%20long-standing%20struggle%20for%20the%20US%20shipbuilding%20industry.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%2C%20as%20O'Rourke%20and%20others%20said%2C%20differences%20between%20building%20commercial%20and%20military%20vessels%2C%20such%20as%20how%20many%20can%20be%20made%2C%20interior%20density%20and%20complexity%2C%20propulsion%20systems%2C%20survivability%2C%20intended%20life%20cycles%2C%20and%20the%20installation%20of%20combat%20systems%2C%20and%20all%20of%20that%20needs%20to%20be%20taken%20into%20account.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223543%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Chinese%20shipyard%20workers%20working%20on%20various%20elements%20of%20shipping%20equipment%20in%20Nantong%2C%20China%2C%20on%20July%208%2C%202024.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66eaea3acfb7f307e572a1e0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222505%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EChina's%20shipbuilding%20empire%20is%20massive%2C%20with%20South%20Korea%20and%20Japan%20second%20and%20third%20in%20the%20world%2C%20respectively.%3Cp%3ECostfoto%2FNurPhoto%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20that%20does%20not%20mean%20there%20aren't%20potential%20lessons%20that%20could%20be%20applicable%20to%20US%20shipbuilding.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20April%2C%20then-Secretary%20of%20the%20Navy%20Carlos%20Del%20Toro%20said%20he%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-navy-secretary-floored-by-ally-south-koreas-shipbuilding-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3Bfloored%26quot%3B%20by%20South%20Korea's%20shipyard%20capabilities%3C%2Fa%3E%20after%20a%20visit%2C%20especially%20digitization%20and%20real-time%20monitoring%20of%20shipbuilding%20progress%2C%20which%20included%20%26quot%3Bregularly%20available%20information%20down%20to%20individual%20pieces%20of%20stock%20materials.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETop%20South%20Korean%20shipbuilding%20executives%20are%20able%20to%20pinpoint%20the%20exact%20day%20when%20ships%20will%20be%20delivered%2C%20he%20noted%20at%20the%20time%2C%20a%20stark%20difference%20from%20the%20severe%20delays%20the%20US%20faces%20in%20shipbuilding%20capacity%2C%20labor%20availability%2C%20and%20resources.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHow%20the%20US%20could%20capitalize%20on%20and%20embrace%20the%20effective%20shipbuilding%20practices%20of%20allies%20like%20Japan%20and%20South%20Korea%20%E2%80%94%20or%20work%20closer%20with%20their%20biggest%20companies%20%E2%80%94%20is%20a%20major%20focal%20point%2C%20as%20the%20US%20and%20its%20Pacific%20partners%20look%20carefully%20at%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchinas-shipbuilding-power-players-making-warships-at-a-rapid-pace-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EChina's%20dominant%20shipbuilding%20empire%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20regional%20security%20concerns.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BJapan%20and%20South%20Korea%20are%20in%20competition%20with%20China%2C%26quot%3B%20O'Rourke%20said%2C%20%26quot%3Bso%20they%20are%20trying%20to%20hold%20onto%20their%20market%20share%20against%20the%20Chinese%20shipbuilding%2C%26quot%3B%20pushing%20them%20to%20make%20their%20shipbuilding%20operations%20as%20effective%20as%20possible.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAutomation%20and%20streamlined%20production%20processes%20are%20key%20to%20achieving%20that.%20South%20Korea%20and%20Japan%20are%2C%20respectively%2C%20the%20second%20and%20third%20largest%20shipbuilders%20behind%20China.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpacific-allies-may-have-answer-to-us-navy-shipbuilding-problem-2025-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1741723856000%2C%22visual%22%3