s%20a%20family%20in%20Portland%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20discovered%20our%20mutual%20love%20of%20arcades%20a%20few%20years%20ago%20when%20we%20visited%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Floved-portland-had-to-leave-moved-to-small-town-oregon-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EPortland%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20It%20was%20much%20hotter%20than%20anticipated%2C%20and%20most%20of%20our%20planned%20activities%20were%20outdoors.%20We%20needed%20something%20to%20do%20to%20get%20us%20out%20of%20the%20100-degree%20afternoon%20temperatures.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20a%20desperate%20search%2C%20I%20found%20Ground%20Kontrol%2C%20a%20two-story%20arcade%20that%20not%20only%20fit%20the%20bill%20for%20an%20air-conditioned%20establishment%20but%20was%20also%20met%20with%20excitement%20from%20all%20three%20of%20my%20teens.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWe%20spent%20much%20of%20the%20afternoon%20there%2C%20enjoying%20our%20favorite%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fxbox-game-pass%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Earcade%20games%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20and%20even%20a%20few%20that%20were%20new%20to%20us.%20I%20was%20surprised%20by%20how%20much%20time%20we%20spent%20in%20the%20pinball%20area%2C%20considering%20it%20was%20never%20something%20they%20gravitated%20to%20before.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%222cfe2fee-ebbb-493b-9d6d-f7406f227c4d%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3EWe%20now%20visit%20arcades%20on%20every%20family%20trip%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOur%20top%20spots%20are%20tiny%20retro%20arcades%20with%20'80s%20music%20and%20games%20like%20%26quot%3BFrogger%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-games-snake-pac-man%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EP