%20a%20break%20from%20the%20action%20(like%20moms).%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWe%20returned%20for%20a%20second%20night%20since%20we%20enjoyed%20it%20so%20much.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a79bfc2d-d7b7-4ecf-9334-bfb08d3f8d8e%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3EWe've%20found%20endless%20benefits%20to%20seeking%20out%20arcades%20on%20trips%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20think%20it's%20something%20about%20being%20together%2C%20yet%20separate%2C%20that%20makes%20arcades%20a%20top%20pick%20for%20us.%20Just%20when%20I%20think%20we're%20all%20sick%20of%20each%20other%2C%20I%20locate%20them%20playing%20multi-player%20%26quot%3BPac-Man.%26quot%3B%20It's%20a%20sibling%20miracle.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EVisiting%20an%20arcade%20offers%20some%20downtime%20without%20being%20stuck%20in%20our%20tiny%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftiny-hotel-room-inside-airport-during-layover-worth-230-2023-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ehotel%20room%2C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20all%20on%20our%20phones.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20we%20visited%20Hungry%20Sasquatch%2FThirsty%20Sasquatch%20on%20a%20recent%20visit%20to%20Vancouver%2C%20Washington%2C%20we%20went%20for%20the%20pizza%20by%20the%20slice.%20Still%2C%20the%20arcade%20games%20allowed%20me%20to%20sit%20and%20enjoy%20a%20local%20brew%20while%20checking%20my%20email.%20We%20spent%20an%20hour%20or%20so%20there%2C%20and%20it%20was%20enough%20of%20a%20reprieve%20to%20get%20us%20out%20and%20exploring%20the%20city%20some%20more%20(after%20an%20ice%20cream%2C%20of%20course).%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere's%20also%20the%20friendly%2C%20low-stakes%20competition%20that%20comes%20with%20an%20arcade%20visit.%20Sometimes%2C%20with%20three%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgen-x-mom-kids-children-different-generations-teach-trends-memes-202