C%20Southwest%20Airlines%20shares%20climbed%20due%20to%20new%20revenue-generating%20initiatives.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20TECH%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Ftechnology%2Ftech-news%2Fwhy-expedia-group-airbnb-and-other-travel-stocks-are-seeing-one-of-the-biggest-ever-fall%2Farticleshow%2F118903245.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Netflix%20Sets%20Remake%20of%20Stephen%20King%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98Cujo%E2%80%99%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1741719985000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F01%2FGettyImages-2170597222.jpg%3Fw%3D1000%26h%3D563%26crop%3D1%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F%3Fp%3D1236334641%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Netflix%20has%20greenlit%20a%20remake%20of%20Stephen%20King%E2%80%99s%20novel%20%E2%80%9CCujo%2C%E2%80%9D%20a%20horror%20story%20about%20a%20mother%20and%20son%20who%20get%20trapped%20in%20their%20car%20while%20protecting%20themselves%20from%20a%20rabid%20dog.%20Roy%20Lee%C2%A0(%E2%80%9CBarbarian%E2%80%9D)%20will%20produce%20the%20reboot%2C%20which%20has%20yet%20to%20attach%20a%20writer%2C%20director%20or%20cast.%20King%E2%80%99s%201981%20book%20was%20first%20adapted%20into%20a%20%5B%E2%80%A6%5D%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Rebecca%20Rubin%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2025%2Ffilm%2Fnews%2Fcujo-remake-netflix-stephen-king-1236334641%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Union%20Minister%20Shares%20Tamil%20Nadu's%20Letter%20On%20PM%20SHRI%20Schools%2C%20Row%20Intensifies%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EUnion%20Education%20Minister%20Dharmendra%20Pradhan%20shared%20a%20letter%20from%20the%20Tamil%20Nadu%20school%20education%20department%20that%20said%20the%20southern%20state%20was%20%26quot%3Bvery%20keen%26quot%3B%20to%20set%20up%20PM%20SHRI%20Schools%2C%20as%20the%20Union%20Minister%20launched%20a%20counter-attack%20against%20the%20DMK%20over%20allegations%20that%20he%20misled%20parliament.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECriticising%20Tamil%20Nadu's%20ruling%20DMK%20government%20for%20%26quot%3Bplaying%20politics%26quot%3B%20over%20the%20three-language%20initiative%20in%20the%20New%20Education%20Policy%20(NEP)%2C%20Mr%20Pradhan%20in%20parliament%20said%20the%20party%20led%20by%20Chief%20Minister%20MK%20Stalin%20was%20%26quot%3Bdishonest%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20(DMK)%20are%20dishonest.%20They%20are%20not%20committed%20to%20the%20students%20of%20Tamil%20Nadu.%20They%20are%20ruining%20the%20future%20of%20Tamil%20Nadu%20students.%20Their%20only%20job%20is%20to%20raise%20language%20barriers.%20They%20are%20doing%20politics.%20They%20are%20making%20mischief.%20They%20are%20undemocratic%20and%20uncivilised%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Pradhan%20said%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20response%2C%20the%20DMK%20initiated%20a%20privilege%20motion%20with%20its%20MP%20Kanimozhi%20NVN%20Somu%20requesting%20Lok%20Sabha%20Speaker%20Om%20Birla%20to%20take%20action%20for%20%26quot%3Bcontempt%20of%20the%20house%26quot%3B.%20The%20DMK%20MP's%20notice%20said%20Mr%20Pradhan's%20claim%20that%20the%20Tamil%20Nadu%20government%20took%20a%20U-turn%20after%20agreeing%20to%20sign%20an%20MoU%20with%20the%20Centre%20to%20accept%20PM%20SHRI%20Schools%20in%20the%20state%20was%20%26quot%3Bfactually%20incorrect%2C%20misleading%20the%20house%20and%20against%20official%20record.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Pradhan%20then%20posted%20the%20letter%20dated%20March%2015%2C%202024%20from%20the%20Tamil%20Nadu%20education%20department%20to%20prove%20the%20point%20he%20made%20in%20the%20house.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B...%20I%20stand%20by%20my%20statement%20made%20in%20the%20Parliament%20and%20am%20sharing%20the%20consent%20letter%20from%20Tamil%20Nadu%20School%20Education%20Department%20dated%2015th%20March%202024.%20DMK%20MPs%20and%20Hon'ble%20CM%20can%20stack%20lies%20as%20high%20as%20they%20want%2C%20but%20the%20truth%20doesn't%20bother%20knocking%20when%20it%20comes%20crashing%20down%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Union%20Education%20Minister%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20DMK%20dispensation%20led%20by%20Hon'ble%20CM%20Stalin%20have%20a%20lot%20to%20answer%20to%20the%20people%20of%20Tamil%20Nadu.%20Raking%20the%20language%20issue%20as%20a%20diversionary%20tactic%20and%20denying%20facts%20as%20per%20their%20convenience%20will%20not%20shield%20their%20governance%20and%20welfare%20deficit.%20Why%20this%20sudden%20change%20of%20stance%20on%20NEP%3F%20Definitely%20for%20political%20brownies%20and%20reviving%20DMK's%20political%20fortunes.%20This%20retrograde%20politics%20of%20DMK%20is%20a%20great%20disservice%20to%20the%20bright%20future%20of%20Tamil%20Nadu%20and%20its%20students%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Pradhan%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EYesterday%2C%20DMK%20MPs%20and%20Hon'ble%20CM%20Stalin%20accused%20me%20of%20misleading%20the%20Parliament%20regarding%20Tamil%20Nadu's%20consent%20for%20establishment%20of%20PM-SHRI%20Schools.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnI%20stand%20by%20my%20statement%20made%20in%20the%20Parliament%20and%20am%20sharing%20the%20consent%20letter%20from%20Tamil%20Nadu%20School%20Education%20Department...%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2Fvp6GtPEp1q%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2Fvp6GtPEp1q%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Dharmendra%20Pradhan%20(%40dpradhanbjp)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fdpradhanbjp%2Fstatus%2F1899469771952787556%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EMarch%2011%2C%202025%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKanimozhi%2C%20the%20DMK%20MP%2C%20today%20told%20reporters%20the%20state%20did%20agree%20on%20setting%20up%20PM%20SHRI%20Schools%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20but%20on%20one%20condition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20had%20said%20that%20we%20agreed%20on%20PM%20SHRI%20Schools%20based%20on%20the%20committee%20recommendations%2C%20then%20only%20the%20%5Bstate%5D%20government%20would%20have%20signed%20the%20MoU%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20reporters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EEducation%20Minister%20Hits%20Back%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETamil%20Nadu%20Education%20Minister%20Anbil%20Mahesh%20refuted%20Mr%20Pradhan's%20allegations%20that%20the%20state%20made%20a%20sudden%20change%20in%20its%20stance%20on%20PM%20SHRI%20Schools.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Mahesh%2C%20pointing%20at%20the%20letter%20shared%20by%20Mr%20Pradhan%2C%20said%20it%20clearly%20mentioned%20that%20a%20committee%20will%20be%20formed%20and%20based%20on%20its%20finding%20the%20state%20would%20decide%20on%20implementing%20the%20Centre's%20initiative.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThose%20who%20are%20trying%20to%20impose%20the%20NEP%20are%20playing%20politics%2C%20not%20us.%20Tamil%20Nadu's%20education%20model%20is%20exemplary%20and%20has%20consistently%20proven%20its%20ability%20to%20shape%20the%20future%20of%20our%20students%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BPlease%20understand%20that%20India's%20diversity%20is%20its%20strength%2C%20not%20weakness.%20You%20should%20rather%20acknowledge%20and%20support%20Tamil%20Nadu's%20right%20to%20choose%20what%20is%20best%20for%20the%20future%20of%20its%20children.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20entire%20controversy%20stems%20from%20the%20debate%20over%20the%20NEP%2C%20particularly%20the%20contentious%20three-language%20policy%2C%20which%20Tamil%20Nadu%20strongly%20opposes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%26quot%3BTamil%20Medium%20Enrolments%20Declining%26quot%3B%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Pradhan%20quoting%20data%20from%20the%20Unified%20District%20Information%20System%20For%20Education%20Plus%20(UDISE%2B)%20said%20enrolments%20in%20Tamil%20medium%20dropped%20from%2065.87%20lakh%20in%202018-19%20to%2046.83%20lakh%20in%202023-24%2C%20a%20reduction%20of%20over%2019.05%20lakh%20students%20in%20five%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%2067%20per%20cent%20of%20students%20are%20now%20in%20English%20medium%20schools%2C%20while%20Tamil%20medium%20enrolment%20has%20dropped%20from%2054%20per%20cent%20(2018-19)%20to%2036%20per%20cent%20(2023-24).%20In%20government%20schools%2C%20English%20medium%20enrolment%20rose%20five%20times%20from%203.4%20lakh%20to%2017.7%20lakh%20in%20just%20five%20years%2C%20and%20Tamil%20medium%20enrolment%20fell%20by%207.3%20lakh%20in%20government-aided%20schools%2C%20reflecting%20a%20deep%20shift%20in%20preference.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThese%20numbers%20reveal%20the%20real%20story%20-%20enrolments%20in%20Tamil%20medium%20are%20on%20a%20continuous%20decline.%20This%20isn't%20just%20a%20shift%20in%20language%20preference%2C%20it's%20a%20colonial%20mindset%20at%20play.%20English%20is%20seen%20as%20the%20gateway%20to%20status%20and%20jobs%2C%20Indian%20languages%20are%20seen%20as%20a%20symbol%20of%20backwardness%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Union%20Minister%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPM%20SHRI%20School%20is%20a%20centrally%20sponsored%20scheme%2C%20intended%20to%20develop%20more%20than%2014%2C500%20schools%20managed%20by%20the%20central%20government%2C%20state%2C%20Union%20Territory%20government%20and%20local%20bodies%20including%20KVS%20and%20NVS.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESHRI%20is%20short%20for%20'Schools%20for%20Rising%20India'.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20objectives%20include%20ensuring%20every%20student%20feels%20welcomed%20and%20cared%20for%2C%20where%20a%20safe%20and%20stimulating%20learning%20environment%20exists%2C%20where%20a%20wide%20range%20of%20learning%20experiences%20are%20offered%2C%20and%20where%20good%20physical%20infrastructure%20and%20appropriate%20resources%20conducive%20to%20learning%20are%20available%20to%20all%20students%2C%20the%20government%20says%20on%20the%20PM%20SHRI%20School%20programme%20website.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1741719780000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.