long%20to%20their%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBalochistan's%20mountainous%20border%20region%20serves%20as%20a%20safe%20haven%20and%20training%20ground%20for%20the%20Baloch%20insurgents%20and%20Islamist%20militants.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHOW%20HAS%20IT%20BECOME%20MORE%20LETHAL%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BLA%20shocked%20the%20country's%20security%20establishment%20when%20it%20barged%20into%20army%20and%20navy%20bases%20in%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20has%20deployed%20women%20suicide%20bombers%2C%20including%20in%20an%20attack%20on%20Chinese%20nationals%20at%20a%20university%20in%20Karachi%20and%20a%20bombing%20in%20southwest%20Balochistan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20umbrella%20group%20of%20several%20Baloch%20ethnic%20groups%20said%20last%20week%20that%20it%20had%20convened%20all%20factions%20in%20a%20bid%20to%20unite%20them%20under%20a%20unified%20military%20structure.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20dormant%20BLA%20splinter%20group%20called%20BLA%20(AZAD)%20became%20active%20in%20recent%20weeks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWHAT%20ARE%20THE%20BLA'S%20TARGETS%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BLA%20often%20targets%20infrastructure%20and%20security%20forces%20in%20Balochistan%2C%20but%20has%20also%20truck%20in%20other%20areas%20-%20most%20notably%20the%20southern%20port%20city%20of%20Karachi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20insurgents%20target%20Pakistan's%20army%20and%20Chinese%20interests%2C%20in%20particular%20the%20strategic%20port%20of%20Gwadar%20on%20the%20Arabian%20Sea%2C%20accusing%20Beijing%20of%20helping%20Islamabad%20to%20exploit%20the%20province.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMilitants%20have%20killed%20Chinese%20citizens%20working%20in%20the%20region%20and%20attacked%20Beijing's%20consulate%20in%20Karachi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BLA%2C%20separately%2C%20was%20also%20at%20the%20centre%20of%20tit-for-tat%20strikes%20last%20year%20between%20Iran%20and%20Pakistan%20over%20what%20they%20called%20militant%20bases%20on%20each%20other's%20territory%2C%20which%20brought%20the%20neighbours%20close%20to%20war.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBALOCHISTAN'S%20SIGNIFICANCE%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBalochistan%20is%20an%20important%20part%20of%20China's%20%2465%20billion%20investment%20in%20the%20China%20Pakistan%20Economic%20Corridor%2C%20a%20wing%20of%20President%20Xi%20Jinping's%20Belt%20and%20Road%20initiative.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20home%20to%20key%20mining%20projects%2C%20including%20Reko%20Diq%2C%20run%20by%20mining%20giant%20Barrick%20Gold%20(ABX.TO)%2C%20and%20believed%20to%20be%20one%20of%20the%20world's%20largest%20gold%20and%20copper%20mines.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChina%20also%20operates%20a%20gold%20and%20copper%20mine%20in%20the%20province.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20decades-old%20insurgency%20has%20continued%20to%20keep%20the%20province%20of%20some%2015%20million%20people%20unstable%20and%20created%20security%20concerns%20around%20Pakistan's%20plans%20to%20access%20untapped%20resources.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20Pakistan's%20largest%20province%20by%20area%2C%20but%20smallest%20by%20population.%20Balochistan%20also%20has%20a%20long%20Arabian%20Sea%20coastline%2C%20not%20far%20from%20the%20Gulf's%20Strait%20of%20Hormuz%20oil%20shipping%20lane.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHundreds%20of%20Baloch%20activists%2C%20many%20of%20them%20women%2C%20have%20protested%20in%20Islamabad%20and%20Balochistan%20over%20alleged%20abuses%20by%20security%20forces%20-%20accusations%20the%20government%20denies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIslamabad%20accuses%20India%20and%20Afghanistan%20of%20backing%20the%20militants%20to%20damage%20Pakistan's%20relations%20with%20China%2C%20a%20charge%20both%20countries%20deny.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1741713240000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2Forqlfh6g_pakista